          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Top the <strong>ciabatta bases</strong> with the <strong>sloppy joe filling</strong> and <strong>grated cheese</strong> and place a <strong>ciabatta lid </strong>on top – these are your<strong> filled ciabattas</strong></p><p>Reserve the pan</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
